Custom Configuration Framework (custom-conf)
============================================
Package: custom-conf-symfony-2.7

This package provides standard configuration of PHP/Symfony (version 2.7) web
applications framework.

In particular, it addresses standard configuration of:
 - PHP5/Apache2 or PHP5/FPM integration (<-> 'custom-conf-php5-...' packages)
 - installation and update via 'composer' (and a dedicated user/group)

It also provides a sample skeleton to have a PHP/Symfony application jump-
started correspondingly.

